text: George I (6 May 1747 – 9 September 1813) was Prince of Waldeck and Pyrmont from 1812 to 1813.He was the son of Karl August, Prince of Waldeck and Pyrmont and Christiane Henriette, Countess Palatine of Zweibrücken Category:1747 births Category:1813 deaths Category:Princes of Waldeck and Pyrmont
